{%- comment -%}
  PFD2 — Advertorial listicle for Magnesium Glycinate | 8x Absorbable. Mid-funnel paid traffic.
  Hook: "5 Bad Habits That Won't Survive Your First Week of High-Absorption Magnesium" — "we're sorry" reframe,
  consequences shaped as guilty pleasures. Audience: mag-aware buyers who've tried cheap oxide and felt nothing.
  Brand voice: declarative, no em dashes, no exclamation points, dry humor.
  Compliance: structure/function claims marked with <sup>*</sup>. No medical/disease claims.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign hero_img      = section.settings.hero_img      | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'
  assign product_img   = section.settings.product_img   | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'
  assign img_1         = section.settings.img_1         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'
  assign img_2         = section.settings.img_2         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'
  assign img_3         = section.settings.img_3         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'
  assign img_4         = section.settings.img_4         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'
  assign img_5         = section.settings.img_5         | default: 'https://www.absorbmore.com/cdn/shop/files/TAC_PDP-Image_Magnesium-Glycinate.png?v=1774483977'

  comment
    Buybox: mirrors the live PDP. Three bottle-count tiers, all priced at $18.20/bottle (35% off $28).
    Selling plans verified 2026-05-24 from live DOM. "Every 2 months" cadence.
    NOTE: 35% off is Memorial Day promo (ends 2026-05-25). Update to 10% base discount after.
  endcomment
  assign cart_1bot     = section.settings.cart_1bot     | default: '/cart/52439421976865:1?selling_plan=691154485537'
  assign cart_2bot     = section.settings.cart_2bot     | default: '/cart/52439422009633:1?selling_plan=691154518305'
  assign cart_3bot     = section.settings.cart_3bot     | default: '/cart/52439422042401:1?selling_plan=691154551073'

  assign price_1bot_per   = section.settings.price_1bot_per   | default: '$18.20/bottle'
  assign price_1bot_was   = section.settings.price_1bot_was   | default: '$28.00'
  assign price_1bot_total = section.settings.price_1bot_total | default: '$18.20 total'
  assign price_1bot_save  = section.settings.price_1bot_save  | default: 'save $9.80'
  assign discount_1bot    = section.settings.discount_1bot    | default: '35'

  assign price_2bot_per   = section.settings.price_2bot_per   | default: '$18.20/bottle'
  assign price_2bot_was   = section.settings.price_2bot_was   | default: '$56.00'
  assign price_2bot_total = section.settings.price_2bot_total | default: '$36.40 total'
  assign price_2bot_save  = section.settings.price_2bot_save  | default: 'save $19.60'
  assign discount_2bot    = section.settings.discount_2bot    | default: '35'

  assign price_3bot_per   = section.settings.price_3bot_per   | default: '$18.20/bottle'
  assign price_3bot_was   = section.settings.price_3bot_was   | default: '$84.00'
  assign price_3bot_total = section.settings.price_3bot_total | default: '$54.60 total'
  assign price_3bot_save  = section.settings.price_3bot_save  | default: 'save $29.40'
  assign discount_3bot    = section.settings.discount_3bot    | default: '35'

  assign rating        = section.settings.rating        | default: '4.0'
  assign review_count  = section.settings.review_count  | default: '80+'
  assign byline        = section.settings.byline        | default: 'By The Absorption Company Editorial'
  assign pub_date      = section.settings.pub_date      | default: 'May 2026'
  assign read_time     = section.settings.read_time     | default: '5 min read'

  comment
    Hero copy. Schema-editable so the H1 can be swapped to message-match each ad creative
    without a code change.
  endcomment
  assign kicker_text   = section.settings.kicker_text   | default: 'Before You Reach for Another Bottle of Magnesium'
  assign headline_html = section.settings.headline_html | default: "We're Sorry In Advance: 5 Bad Habits That Won't Survive Your First Week of <em>High-Absorption Magnesium</em>."
  assign dek_html      = section.settings.dek_html      | default: '<p>Most magnesium on the shelf is magnesium oxide, which absorbs at roughly 4%. Ours is <b>magnesium glycinate, formulated to absorb 8x more</b>.<sup>*</sup> Fair warning about what happens when it actually works.</p>'
  assign lede_text     = section.settings.lede_text     | default: 'Before you start, we owe you five honest warnings about the things you have been quietly enjoying that high-absorption magnesium is about to take away.'
  assign hero_cta_text = section.settings.hero_cta_text | default: 'See plans'

  comment
    Optional asset slots. All render hide-if-empty so the page still works pre-asset.
  endcomment
  assign ugc_video_url     = section.settings.ugc_video_url
  assign ugc_video_poster  = section.settings.ugc_video_poster
  assign ugc_video_caption = section.settings.ugc_video_caption | default: 'Watch: real customer, 3 weeks in.'
  assign founder_name      = section.settings.founder_name
  assign founder_title     = section.settings.founder_title     | default: 'Founder, The Absorption Company'
  assign founder_quote     = section.settings.founder_quote
  assign founder_img       = section.settings.founder_img

  assign klaviyo_company_id = section.settings.klaviyo_company_id
  assign klaviyo_list_id    = section.settings.klaviyo_list_id
  assign email_head         = section.settings.email_head    | default: 'Not ready yet?'
  assign email_sub          = section.settings.email_sub     | default: 'Get the magnesium absorption brief in your inbox. Why oxide fails, why glycinate works, and what 8x absorption actually means.'
  assign email_cta          = section.settings.email_cta     | default: 'Send it to me'
-%}

<style>
  .pfd2 { --ink:#0B1220; --paper:#FBFAF6; --cream:#F4EFE4; --line:#E4DFD2; --blue:#4659FF; --blue-deep:#2C3FD9; --red:#E1225C; --gold:#C99A33; --mute:#5E6470;
    color:var(--ink); background:var(--paper);  -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased; line-height:1.55; font-size:17px; }
  .pfd2 *{box-sizing:border-box}
  .pfd2 img{max-width:100%;display:block;height:auto}
  .pfd2 a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
  .pfd2 .wrap{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px}
  .pfd2 .wrap-wide{max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 22px}

  /* ---------- DISCLOSURE BAR ---------- */
  .pfd2-disc{background:#0B1220;color:#fff;font-size:12px;text-align:center;padding:8px 16px;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700}
  .pfd2-disc span{opacity:.7;margin-right:8px}

  /* ---------- MASTHEAD ---------- */
  .pfd2-mast{background:#fff;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:14px 0}
  .pfd2-mast__row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px}
  .pfd2-mast__logo{font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.01em;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-mast__tag{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--mute);font-weight:600}

  /* ---------- ARTICLE HEAD ---------- */
  .pfd2-art{padding:36px 0 24px}
  .pfd2-art__kicker{font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--red);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 14px}
  .pfd2-art h1{font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(30px,5.6vw,46px);line-height:1.08;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 16px;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-art h1 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--blue)}
  .pfd2-art__dek{font-size:clamp(17px,2.2vw,20px);line-height:1.45;color:#2D3340;margin:0 0 22px;font-weight:400}
  .pfd2-art__dek b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
  .pfd2-art__meta{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px 18px;align-items:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--mute);border-top:1px solid var(--line);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding:12px 0;margin:0 0 24px}
  .pfd2-art__meta b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}
  .pfd2-art__meta span{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}

  /* ---------- HERO IMAGE ---------- */
  .pfd2-heroimg{margin:0 0 28px;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--cream)}
  .pfd2-heroimg img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:16/10;object-fit:cover}
  .pfd2-heroimg figcaption{font-size:13px;color:var(--mute);padding:10px 4px 0;line-height:1.4}
  .pfd2-heroimg figcaption b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:600}

  /* ---------- BODY ---------- */
  .pfd2-body{padding:0 0 16px}
  .pfd2-body p{margin:0 0 18px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;color:#1E2330}
  .pfd2-body p.lede{font-size:19px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--ink);font-weight:500}
  .pfd2-body p.lede::first-letter{font-size:54px;font-weight:700;float:left;line-height:.9;padding:6px 10px 0 0;color:var(--blue)}
  .pfd2-body strong{font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}

  /* ---------- SECTION IMAGE ---------- */
  .pfd2-secimg{margin:8px 0 22px;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--cream)}
  .pfd2-secimg img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/3;object-fit:cover}
  .pfd2-secimg figcaption{font-size:12px;color:var(--mute);padding:8px 4px 0;line-height:1.4;font-style:italic}

  /* ---------- NUMBERED SORRY BLOCKS ---------- */
  .pfd2-sorry{padding:28px 0 28px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .pfd2-sorry__num{font-size:64px;font-weight:700;line-height:1;color:var(--blue);margin:0 0 6px;letter-spacing:-.03em}
  .pfd2-sorry__kicker{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.18em;color:var(--mute);font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px}
  .pfd2-sorry h2{font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,32px);line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 18px;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-sorry h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--blue)}
  .pfd2-sorry p{margin:0 0 16px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;color:#1E2330}
  .pfd2-sorry__pull{border-left:4px solid var(--blue);background:var(--cream);padding:16px 18px;margin:18px 0;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--ink);border-radius:0 4px 4px 0}
  .pfd2-sorry__pull b{font-weight:700;color:var(--blue-deep)}
  .pfd2-sorry__pull .stat{display:block;font-size:28px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue-deep);line-height:1;margin:0 0 4px}

  /* ---------- INLINE CTA (after sorry #3) ---------- */
  .pfd2-inline-cta{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-radius:8px;padding:24px 22px;margin:24px 0;text-align:center}
  .pfd2-inline-cta p{margin:0 0 14px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.45;color:#E8ECF4}
  .pfd2-inline-cta p b{color:#fff;font-weight:700}
  .pfd2-inline-cta a{display:inline-block;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;padding:13px 24px;border-radius:6px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em}
  .pfd2-inline-cta__price{display:block;font-size:12px;color:#9AA4BC;margin-top:8px;letter-spacing:.04em}
  .pfd2-inline-cta__price b{color:#fff;font-weight:700}

  /* ---------- PRODUCT REVEAL ---------- */
  .pfd2-reveal{background:var(--cream);padding:48px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--line);margin-top:32px}
  .pfd2-reveal__kicker{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--red);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 12px;text-align:center}
  .pfd2-reveal h2{font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,40px);line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin:0 0 16px;color:var(--ink);text-align:center}
  .pfd2-reveal h2 em{font-style:italic;color:var(--blue)}
  .pfd2-reveal__sub{text-align:center;font-size:17px;line-height:1.55;color:#2D3340;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 28px}
  .pfd2-reveal__three{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 0}
  @media(min-width:680px){.pfd2-reveal__three{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
  .pfd2-reveal__card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:18px 16px;text-align:center}
  .pfd2-reveal__card b{display:block;font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue);line-height:1;margin:0 0 6px}
  .pfd2-reveal__card span{display:block;font-size:13px;color:var(--mute);line-height:1.4;font-weight:500}

  /* ---------- BUYBOX ---------- */
  .pfd2-buy{padding:48px 0;background:#fff}
  .pfd2-buy__head{text-align:center;margin:0 0 22px}
  .pfd2-buy__kicker{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--red);font-weight:800;margin:0 0 10px}
  .pfd2-buy h2{font-weight:700;font-size:clamp(26px,4.6vw,36px);line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 8px;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-buy__sub{font-size:15px;color:var(--mute);margin:0 auto;max-width:520px}
  .pfd2-buy__label{font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.14em;color:var(--mute);font-weight:700;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 10px;padding:0 4px}

  .pfd2-buy__list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;background:#fff}
  .pfd2-row{position:relative;display:block;padding:18px 18px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:#fff;color:var(--ink);transition:background .15s ease}
  .pfd2-row:last-child{border-bottom:0}
  .pfd2-row:hover{background:#FBFAF6}
  .pfd2-row--best{background:#F4EFE4}
  .pfd2-row--best:hover{background:#EDE6D4}

  .pfd2-row__top{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:14px;margin:0 0 6px}
  .pfd2-row__left{flex:1;min-width:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
  .pfd2-row__namerow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
  .pfd2-row__radio{width:18px;height:18px;border:2px solid #B7BBC4;border-radius:999px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#fff;margin-right:2px}
  .pfd2-row--best .pfd2-row__radio{border-color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-row--best .pfd2-row__radio:after{content:"";width:9px;height:9px;background:var(--ink);border-radius:999px;display:block}
  .pfd2-row__name{font-size:19px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.1}
  .pfd2-row__pill{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-size:10px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.10em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 9px;border-radius:4px;line-height:1}
  .pfd2-row__pill--save{background:var(--red);color:#fff}
  .pfd2-row__pill--pop{background:#4E78D1;color:#fff}
  .pfd2-row__pill--best{background:#4E78D1;color:#fff}
  .pfd2-row__desc{font-size:14px;line-height:1.4;color:#3D4452;max-width:380px;margin:0}
  .pfd2-row__assure{font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;color:var(--mute);margin:0}

  .pfd2-row__right{text-align:right;flex:0 0 auto;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-end;gap:2px;min-width:120px}
  .pfd2-row__per{font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);line-height:1.1;white-space:nowrap}
  .pfd2-row__totline{font-size:13px;color:#3D4452;white-space:nowrap}
  .pfd2-row__was{text-decoration:line-through;color:var(--mute);margin-right:4px}
  .pfd2-row__save{font-size:13px;color:var(--blue-deep);font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap}

  .pfd2-row__cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:11px 18px;border-radius:6px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-top:10px}
  .pfd2-row--best .pfd2-row__cta{background:var(--blue)}
  .pfd2-row__cta:after{content:" →";margin-left:6px}

  @media(max-width:480px){
    .pfd2-row__top{flex-direction:column;align-items:stretch}
    .pfd2-row__right{align-items:flex-start;text-align:left;flex-direction:row;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px 12px}
    .pfd2-row__per{font-size:20px}
  }

  .pfd2-buy__assure{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:10px 20px;justify-content:center;align-items:center;font-size:13px;color:var(--mute);margin:16px auto 0;max-width:720px}
  .pfd2-buy__assure span{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
  .pfd2-buy__assure svg{width:16px;height:16px;color:var(--blue)}

  /* ---------- REVIEWS BAND ---------- */
  .pfd2-rev{padding:44px 0;background:var(--cream);border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .pfd2-rev__head{text-align:center;margin:0 0 24px}
  .pfd2-rev__kicker{font-size:11px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:var(--mute);font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px}
  .pfd2-rev h2{font-size:clamp(22px,3.6vw,28px);font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-rev__stars-row{display:flex;justify-content:center;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:14px;color:var(--mute)}
  .pfd2-stars{display:inline-block;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:1px;font-size:16px}
  .pfd2-stars:before{content:"★★★★★"}
  .pfd2-rev__grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:14px;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
  @media(min-width:720px){.pfd2-rev__grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)}}
  .pfd2-quote{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:6px;padding:18px 18px}
  .pfd2-quote__stars{margin:0 0 8px}
  .pfd2-quote p{font-size:16px;line-height:1.55;color:#1E2330;margin:0 0 12px}
  .pfd2-quote__name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-quote__verif{font-size:12px;color:var(--mute);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;margin-top:2px}
  .pfd2-quote__verif svg{width:13px;height:13px;color:var(--blue)}

  /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
  .pfd2-faq{padding:48px 0;background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .pfd2-faq__head{text-align:center;margin:0 0 24px}
  .pfd2-faq h2{font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,32px);font-weight:700;margin:0;color:var(--ink)}
  .pfd2-faq__list{max-width:720px;margin:0 auto}
  .pfd2-faq__item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  .pfd2-faq__item summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;padding:18px 36px 18px 0;font-size:16px;font-weight:600;color:var(--ink);position:relative}
  .pfd2-faq__item summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
  .pfd2-faq__item summary:after{content:"+";position:absolute;right:6px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);font-size:22px;color:var(--blue);font-weight:700;line-height:1}
  .pfd2-faq__item[open] summary:after{content:"–"}
  .pfd2-faq__item p{margin:0 0 18px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#2D3340}

  /* ---------- CLOSE / FINAL CTA ---------- */
  .pfd2-close{padding:56px 0;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;text-align:center}
  .pfd2-close__kicker{font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.16em;color:#A4B0CF;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 10px}
  .pfd2-close h2{font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,40px);font-weight:700;margin:0 0 12px;color:#fff;line-height:1.1}
  .pfd2-close h2 em{font-style:italic;color:#9EA9FF}
  .pfd2-close p{font-size:16px;color:#C9D1E2;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 22px;line-height:1.5}
  .pfd2-close a{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;padding:15px 28px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em}
  .pfd2-close a:after{content:" →";margin-left:6px}

  /* ---------- DISCLAIMER ---------- */
  .pfd2-disclaim{padding:24px 0 80px;background:#fff;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .pfd2-disclaim p{font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--mute);max-width:720px;margin:0 auto 10px}
  .pfd2-disclaim a{color:var(--blue-deep);text-decoration:underline}

  /* ---------- HERO ABOVE-FOLD RATING + CTA ROW ---------- */
  .pfd2-hero-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px 16px;margin:0 0 18px}
  .pfd2-hero-row__rating{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:13px;color:var(--mute)}
  .pfd2-hero-row__rating b{color:var(--ink);font-weight:700}
  .pfd2 a.pfd2-hero-row__cta{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;background:var(--blue);color:#fff;padding:11px 18px;border-radius:6px;font-weight:700;font-size:13px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;min-height:44px}
  .pfd2 a.pfd2-hero-row__cta:after{content:" ↓";margin-left:6px}
  .pfd2 a.pfd2-hero-row__cta:hover{background:var(--blue-deep);color:#fff}

  /* ---------- UGC VIDEO ---------- */
  .pfd2-ugc{margin:0 0 28px;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;background:#0B1220;position:relative}
  .pfd2-ugc video{width:100%;display:block;aspect-ratio:9/16;max-height:640px;object-fit:cover;background:#0B1220}
  @media(min-width:680px){.pfd2-ugc video{aspect-ratio:4/5;max-height:720px}}
  .pfd2-ugc figcaption{font-size:13px;color:var(--mute);padding:10px 4px 0;line-height:1.4}
