        <h2>Questions, honestly answered.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pfd2-faq__list">
        <details class="pfd2-faq__item">
          <summary>What makes this different from the magnesium I already take?</summary>
          <p>The form. Most magnesium on the shelf is <b>magnesium oxide</b>, which absorbs at roughly 4%. Ours is <b>magnesium glycinate</b>, bound to the amino acid glycine, which your gut already absorbs efficiently. The result: <b>8x more absorption</b> than the standard.<sup>*</sup> If you have been taking magnesium for a while and felt nothing, this is usually why.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="pfd2-faq__item">
          <summary>When will I feel it?</summary>
          <p>Most customers notice an easier wind-down the first night they take it. Soreness, mood, and snack-craving changes typically show up within the first one to two weeks as serum magnesium levels build.<sup>*</sup></p>
        </details>
        <details class="pfd2-faq__item">
          <summary>Will it make me groggy in the morning?</summary>
          <p>No. Unlike melatonin, magnesium glycinate does not sedate you. It supports your body's own wind-down pathway through GABA, which means you fall asleep because you are actually tired and wake up rested, not foggy.<sup>*</sup></p>
        </details>
        <details class="pfd2-faq__item">
          <summary>Does it cause a laxative effect?</summary>
          <p>No. The laxative effect people associate with magnesium comes from <b>magnesium oxide</b> (and citrate at higher doses) when the unabsorbed mineral draws water into the gut. Magnesium glycinate is well-absorbed and does not have that effect at our recommended dose.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="pfd2-faq__item">
          <summary>Can I take it with other supplements or medications?</summary>
          <p>Magnesium glycinate is broadly safe and pairs well with most supplements. As with any new supplement, talk to your doctor first if you are pregnant, nursing, or on prescription medication, especially blood pressure or muscle relaxants.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="pfd2-faq__item">
          <summary>What if it does not work for me?</summary>
          <p>Every order is backed by a <b>30-day money-back guarantee</b>. If you do not feel a difference, email us within 30 days of delivery for a full refund.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
